### Apply Leave (employee)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Casual",
  "startDate": "2026-03-29",
  "endDate": "2026-03-30",
  "reason": "Personal work"
}

### Get My Leaves
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/my

### Get Leave Balance
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/balance

### Get Pending Leaves (admin/manager)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/pending

### Approve Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reject Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient balance"
}

### Holidays list
GET http://localhost:3005/api/holidays

### Create Holiday (admin)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/holidays
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holi",
  "date": "2026-03-30",
  "type": "public",
  "description": "Festival of colors"
}

### Employee Detail (admin/manager)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID

### Attendance History (admin/manager or employee)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/attendance/history?employeeId=EMPLOYEE_ID&page=1&limit=25

### Attendance History (filtered)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/attendance/history?employeeId=EMPLOYEE_ID&status=Late&start=2026-03-01&end=2026-03-31&page=1&limit=25

### Bulk Shift Assignment (admin)
PATCH http://localhost:3005/api/work-schedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": ["EMPLOYEE_ID_1", "EMPLOYEE_ID_2"],
  "shiftType": "FT_MAIN"
}

### Tracker - Today (employee)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/today

### Tracker - Submit Today (employee)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/today
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "initial": "Started daily check-ins and reviewed pending tasks.",
  "onIt": "Working on task board updates.",
  "impact": "Cleared 3 pending items.",
  "notes": "Need confirmation on client schedule.",
  "issues": "Awaiting approval from manager."
}

### Tracker History (employee)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/history?page=1&limit=10

### Tracker Admin List
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker?date=2026-03-31

### Tracker Analytics
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/analytics

### Tracker Employee Detail
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/employee/EMPLOYEE_ID

### Weekly Tracker - Get Week (employee)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/weekly?year=2026&week=14

### Weekly Tracker - Submit Week (employee)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/weekly
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": 2026,
  "weekNumber": 14,
  "g1": { "target": 10, "actual": 6, "notes": "Calls logged" },
  "g2": { "target": 8, "actual": 5, "notes": "Leads added" },
  "g3": { "target": 12, "actual": 9, "notes": "Follow-ups" },
  "g4": { "target": 3, "actual": 1, "notes": "Closures" },
  "glTours": { "target": 4, "actual": 2, "locations": "Kora, MWB" },
  "initial": "Started week with onboarding targets.",
  "onIt": "Field visits and pipeline cleanup.",
  "impact": "Closed 2 leads.",
  "notes": "Need more site visit slots.",
  "issues": "Delay in approvals.",
  "status": "submitted"
}

### Weekly Tracker - Admin List
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/weekly?year=2026&week=14

### Weekly Tracker - Review
PATCH http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/weekly/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackerId": "TRACKER_ID",
  "isGoodWeek": true,
  "adminNotes": "Good progress overall.",
  "adminImpact": "Strong closures.",
  "adminIssues": "Watch missed follow-ups."
}

### Weekly Tracker - Analytics
GET http://localhost:3005/api/tracker/weekly/analytics?year=2026&week=14
